---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Carina Property Purchase | Edwards & Smith Success Story"
  description="See how Edwards & Smith secured this Carina property for our client with very specific requirements. Expert buyers agent service in Brisbane."
>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="property-hero section">
      <div class="hero-image">
        <img src="/assets/images/carina-4152.jpg" alt="Carina 4152 property purchased by Edwards & Smith" />
      </div>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="breadcrumb">
          <a href="/">Home</a> / <a href="/recent-purchases">Recent Purchases</a> / <a href="/brisbane/recent-purchases">Brisbane</a> / <span>Carina</span>
        </div>
        <h1>Carina, 4152 - Brisbane</h1>
        <p class="property-subtitle">Secured for client with very specific requirements after extensive searching</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Property Overview -->
    <section class="property-overview section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="overview-grid">
          <div class="overview-main">
            <h2>The Success Story</h2>
            <p class="lead-text">
              Our client came to us after spending some time searching for the perfect home. They were after something very specific in the Carina area, and the competitive Brisbane market made finding the right match challenging.
            </p>

            <h3>What We Did</h3>
            <ul class="success-points">
              <li>Conducted comprehensive market analysis of Carina property trends</li>
              <li>Identified properties matching their specific criteria</li>
              <li>Performed detailed due diligence on property condition and local market values</li>
              <li>Negotiated strategic purchase on behalf of our client</li>
              <li>Managed the entire settlement process for a smooth transaction</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Why Carina?</h3>
            <p>
              Carina offers an excellent balance of established character, quality schools, and convenient access to Brisbane CBD. Our client chose this suburb for its leafy streets, strong community, and proximity to major shopping and employment hubs.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="overview-sidebar">
            <div class="property-card">
              <h3>Property Details</h3>
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="label">Location:</span>
                <span class="value">Carina, QLD 4152</span>
              </div>
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="label">Region:</span>
                <span class="value">Brisbane</span>
              </div>
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="label">Service Type:</span>
                <span class="value">Full Buyers Agent Service</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cta-card">
              <h4>Looking to Buy in Brisbane?</h4>
              <p>Let us help you secure your dream property like we did for this client.</p>
              <a href="/book-free-consultation" class="button-primary">Book Free Consultation</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Suburb Insights -->
    <section class="suburb-insights section alt-bg">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Carina Suburb Insights</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">Why our clients love Carina and what makes this suburb exceptional for property buyers.</p>

        <div class="insights-grid">
          <div class="insight-card">
            <div class="rating">8/10</div>
            <h3>Character & Heritage</h3>
            <p>Charming mix of classic Queenslanders and modern homes. Tree-lined streets with established gardens create a distinctive character that appeals to many buyers.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="insight-card">
            <div class="rating">9/10</div>
            <h3>Family & Schools</h3>
            <p>Excellent schools including Carina State School and nearby Bulimba State Secondary College. Family-friendly parks and safe, quiet streets throughout the suburb.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="insight-card">
            <div class="rating">9/10</div>
            <h3>Lifestyle & Amenities</h3>
            <p>Westfield Carindale shopping center is one of Brisbane's largest. Local cafés, restaurants, and essential services within easy reach. Great suburban lifestyle with urban convenience.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="insight-card">
            <div class="rating">8/10</div>
            <h3>Investment Potential</h3>
            <p>Strong historical capital growth in the eastern suburbs. High rental demand from families and professionals. Established suburb with limited new development maintains property values.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="insight-card">
            <div class="rating">8/10</div>
            <h3>Connectivity & Transport</h3>
            <p>Excellent bus connections to CBD and surrounding suburbs. Easy access to Gateway Motorway. 15-20 minutes to Brisbane CBD during off-peak times.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="insight-card">
            <div class="rating">9/10</div>
            <h3>Community & Safety</h3>
            <p>Well-established, tight-knit community with regular events. Low crime rates and family-oriented atmosphere. Active local groups and community engagement.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Client Testimonial -->
    <section class="testimonial-section section">
      <div class="container-narrow">
        <div class="testimonial-feature">
          <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
          <blockquote>
            <p>After searching for the perfect home with very specific requirements, Edwards & Smith's expertise in the Carina market made all the difference. They understood exactly what we needed and delivered.</p>
          </blockquote>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <p class="author-name">Edwards & Smith Client</p>
            <p class="author-title">Carina, Brisbane</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="faq-section section alt-bg">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Carina Property Buying FAQs</h2>
        <div class="faq-grid">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Why is Carina popular with home buyers?</h3>
            <p>Carina offers excellent schools, established character homes, proximity to Westfield Carindale, and easy access to Brisbane CBD. The leafy streets and family-friendly atmosphere make it highly sought-after.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What types of properties are available in Carina?</h3>
            <p>Carina features a diverse mix including classic Queenslanders, post-war homes, and modern family residences. Properties range from renovators to beautifully updated homes on generous land sizes.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How competitive is the Carina property market?</h3>
            <p>Moderately to highly competitive for quality family homes. Well-presented properties often attract multiple buyers. Having a buyers agent with local knowledge provides a significant advantage.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What should I consider when buying in Carina?</h3>
            <p>Consider proximity to schools, land size, property condition, and potential for renovation or extension. Some streets are quieter than others. A buyers agent can help identify the best opportunities.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How can Edwards & Smith help me buy in Carina?</h3>
            <p>We provide local market expertise, property search services, professional negotiation, detailed due diligence, and complete settlement support. We specialise in finding properties that match specific buyer requirements.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Is Carina a good investment suburb?</h3>
            <p>Yes, Carina has strong fundamentals: established suburb, excellent schools, proximity to major shopping and CBD, and consistent rental demand. The eastern suburbs have shown solid capital growth historically.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Related Properties -->
    <section class="related-properties section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Other Brisbane Properties We've Secured</h2>
        <div class="properties-grid">
          <a href="/recent-purchases/brisbane/carina-heights-4152" class="property-card-link">
            <div class="property-card-small">
              <img src="/assets/images/carina-heights-4152.jpg" alt="Carina Heights property" loading="lazy" />
              <h3>Carina Heights, 4152</h3>
              <p>Purchased for time-poor professional after 12-month search</p>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a href="/recent-purchases/brisbane/camp-hill-4152" class="property-card-link">
            <div class="property-card-small">
              <img src="/assets/images/camp-hill-4152.webp" alt="Camp Hill property" loading="lazy" />
              <h3>Camp Hill, 4152</h3>
              <p>First home buyer secured dream property</p>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a href="/brisbane/recent-purchases" class="property-card-link">
            <div class="property-card-small view-all">
              <h3>View All Brisbane Purchases</h3>
              <p>See our complete track record →</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section class="cta-section section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Ready to Find Your Dream Property?</h2>
        <p>Let us help you secure your next home or investment property</p>
        <a href="/book-free-consultation" class="button-primary">Book Free Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .property-hero {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .hero-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 400px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .property-hero .container {
    padding-top: 30px;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .breadcrumb a {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .breadcrumb a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .property-hero h1 {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .property-subtitle {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }

  .property-overview {
    background-color: var(--white);
  }

  .overview-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 50px;
  }

  .lead-text {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .overview-main h2 {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .overview-main h3 {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    margin-top: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .success-points {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  .success-points li {
    padding: 12px 0 12px 30px;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .success-points li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--primary-green);
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .overview-sidebar {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .property-card {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    padding: 25px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-green);
  }

  .property-card h3 {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .detail-item {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 12px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
  }

  .detail-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .detail-item .label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .detail-item .value {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .cta-card {
    background-color: var(--primary-green);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 25px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-card h4 {
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .cta-card p {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .suburb-insights {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
  }

  .suburb-insights h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

